title: #92Noon! DolemanMemories/Coleman/Studwell
description: The sad news of Vikings/NFL great Chris Doleman's passing led to appearances by Greg Coleman and Scott Studwell to share stories of their former teammate and longtime friend. Gophers vibe heavy on show, too, as Mike Grimm is in on Hoops, former TE Ben Utecht offers Superbowl Stories, and Gopher Hockey coach Bob Motzko wraps the show!
